Chain of Responsibility
like a pipeline to authenticate, login, ... user on a website

Problem:
Need to pass a request through multiple handlers until one handles it.

Core idea:
Link handlers in a chain; each one decides to handle or forward.
it's like use link list on some classes

Roles:
Handler,            abstract class to implement link connection
ConcreteHandler,    sub class to implement each steps
Client

When not to use:
When the receiver is always known or the chain adds unnecessary complexity.

