Observer

Problem:
Need to notify multiple objects automatically when one object changes.
like charts,sheets,... based on another source obj

Core idea:
Subject keeps a list of observers and notifies them on change.

Roles:
Subject,            a class that know how add,remove observers on list to track
Observer,           an Interface to match observers classes
ConcreteSubject,    our source class
ConcreteObserver    our observer classes

When not to use:
When updates are simple, tightly controlled, or too many notifications would cause issues.

