Mediator

Problem:
Many objects communicate in messy, tightly coupled ways.
like a complex form (each parts need communicate each-others)

Core idea:
Centralize communication through a mediator.

Roles:
Mediator,           abstract class that define mediator
ConcreteMediator,   the class that stand at the middle
Colleague           who communicate to mediator

When not to use:
When interactions are simple and a mediator would become unnecessary overhead.

Note: we can implement mediator by observer
      in this situation we set mediator's methods as observer
      we call it EVENT HANDLER

