State

Problem:
An object behaves differently depending on its current state.
like Tool on photoshop (we have many if/else)

Core idea:
Move state-specific behavior into separate state objects.

Roles:
Context,         where we use tools (canvas class)
State,           like Tool interface
ConcreteState    like each tools

When not to use:
When there are only a few simple conditions and separate state classes would be overkill.

